page.title: 01Bransgore Village
page.content: Bransgore is situated North-East of Christchurch and has grown a lot in recent years.In the area that we surveyed there are shops, a garage, public houses, schools, many farms and housing which includes very old cottages and some very modern designs. A visitor to the area would notice the green countryside on either side of the narrow lanes. Picturesque farms with quaint farmers cottages very close to the lanes. The land is low lying and tends to hold water a particular problem in heavy rain. The type of person who lives in this area would be a farm worker or someone who likes to be close to the countryside and who may work in the many towns nearby.
